Invocation Name: thingee tech talk
des: Listen to Thingee Tech-Talk episodes on Alexa! Tech-Talk are 2 to 3 minute videos that bring you the latest advances in digital technology. From Apple news to voice assistants, Tech-Talk brings to you all the latest in technology and how that tech can be used in healthcare settings.
